    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly sought-after 3.8L DFI flat-six powerplant. This specimen maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a documented history showing zero bore scoring. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. Performance is optimized via PASM active damping and cross-drilled rotors clamped by four-piston monoblock calipers. The undercarriage is immaculate, showing no signs of thermal cycling fatigue or fluid seepage. A true purist\u2019s example with a meticulous service pedigree ensuring mechanical integrity at the highest level.",
