    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, coupled with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS unit has been fully serviced with Beisan components for optimal timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The undercarriage is immaculate, showing no signs of oxidation, bushing fatigue, or fluid seepage. With its original factory suspension geometry and pristine interior ergonomics, this M3 represents a superlative example of the chassis' peak performance.",
